text: Karayar () is a rural locality (a village) in Allaguvatsky Selsoviet, Sterlibashevsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 64 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 30 km from Sterlibashevo, 5 km from Nizhny Allaguvat. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlibashevsky District
title: Karayar, Sterlibashevsky District, Republic of Bashkortostan
